        <div class="hero-content">
          <ul class="benefits-list">
            <li>All Computer Types (Windows & Mac)</li>
            <li>Complete Virus & Malware Removal</li>
            <li>30-Minute Mobile Service</li>
            <li>Performance Restoration</li>
            <li>We Come to Your Location</li>
          </ul>
          
          <div class="cta-group">
            <a href="tel:4024166942" class="btn btn-primary btn-large" aria-label="Call now for virus removal service in Dallas Fort Worth">
