          <p>Complete removal of viruses, trojans, worms, and other malicious software. We clean your system thoroughly and restore optimal performance.</p>
          <div class="warranty-tag">Complete Removal</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="device-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg role="img" aria-label="Samsung Galaxy repair icon" width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Malware & Spyware</h3>
          <p>Remove all types of malware including spyware, adware, and browser hijackers. Protect your privacy and secure your data.</p>
          <div class="warranty-tag">90-Day Warranty</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="device-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg role="img" aria-label="iPad tablet repair icon" width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
